com.raweng.built

Class BuiltObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.raweng.built.BuiltObject

  • public class BuiltObject
extends java.lang.Object
    BuiltObject is used to create, update and delete built object on the built.io server.

    raw engineering, Inc
